  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Scope:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Identify and follow up on new business opportunities</li><li>Maintain regular contact with clients to understand logistics needs</li><li>Coordinate with operations and customer service to ensure smooth shipments</li><li>Update sales activities in CRM system</li><li>Attend client meetings and networking events</li><li>Achieve monthly sales targets and support revenue growth</li><li>Stay updated on industry trends and pricing</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Logistics, Supply Chain, Business, or related field</li><li>1–2 years of sales or customer service experience in logistics/freight forwarding</li><li>Fresh graduates are welcome</li><li>Strong communication and teamwork skills</li><li>Self-motivated and results-driven</li><li>Proficient in MS Office</li><li>Knowledge of Incoterms and air/sea freight documentation is a plus</li></ul><p><u><strong>Other Information:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Basic Salary: $3,000</li><li>Transport Allowance: $900</li><li>Handphone Allowance: $100</li><li>Commission: 30% of job profit after first $10,000 target met</li><li>Location: Changi Business Park</li><li>Timing: 8.30am to 5.30pm</li></ul><p>Interested candidates please kindly send CV to 89524450</p><p>Lee Mei Kiew Geraldine<br />CEI Reg: R1331173<br />Link2 Manpower Pte Ltd<br />EA License No: 22C1131</p>",
